    <item>
      <title>日本人口下降迫使巴士公司设立对冲基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/japanese-bus-group-sets-up-forex-fund-to-survive-population-fall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本农村公交线路运营商 Ryobi Holdings Co. 的一个子公司正在设立一只专门从事外汇交易的人工智能对冲基金，以应对东京以外地区人口急剧下降带来的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/japanese-bus-group-sets-up-forex-fund-to-survive-population-fall</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 02:34:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>首席执行官表示，随着关税上调，GlobalWafers 将推动海外扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/globalwafers-must-go-global-as-tariffs-rise-worldwide-ceo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了应对芯片材料关税上调，环球晶圆公司正积极在海外扩张制造业务，这凸显出人们越来越预期未来几年针锋相对的贸易措施将扰乱半导体供应链。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/globalwafers-must-go-global-as-tariffs-rise-worldwide-ceo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
